#------------------------------------------------------------
#### Updating firmware with fwupd
### Are you tired of having to flash a bootable disk to a USB?
### Did the manufacturor give you a .exe to update your BIOS but you are on Linux?
### Here is the solution using fwupd's fwupdmgr command

## Check for updates
fwupdmgr refresh --force
fwupdmgr get-updates

## Update firmware, it may prompt you to restart
fwupdmgr update

